data.description: If the charm of a ranch-style abode appeals to you, this exquisitely updated 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with an attached single-car garage might be your perfect match. A notable perk of this neighborhood is the absence of an HOA, granting you added freedom and flexibility with your property. Situated conveniently near Interstate 26 and Highway 78, this home ensures that shopping centers, restaurants, medical facilities, and prominent employers like Mercedes, Boeing, and Cummins are only a brief drive away.The house greets you with a newly painted front porch, while the rear boasts a brand-new porch, complemented by a modern sliding glass door. The residence is freshlypainted throughout and features new laminate flooring for a contemporary look and easy maintenance.  Cooking enthusiasts will delight in the updated kitchen, which showcases new tile flooring, a new sink, and brand-new appliances including a refrigerator and stove, all installed in 2021.
